OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDelays in state pension    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpayments 'causing anxiety' 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Hundreds of new pensioners could face  
OL,6, anxiety and stress owing to delays in  
OL,7, payments of their state pension,       
OL,8, campaigners have said.                 
OL,10,FThe Department for Work and Pensions   
OL,11,Fadmitted that the pandemic and staffing
OL,12,Fissues had caused backlogs in payments 
OL,13,Fto those reaching the age of 66.       
OL,15,FIt is understood that the number       
OL,16,Faffected is in the low thousands, and  
OL,17,Fofficials have apologised to them.     
OL,19,FOne charity said that the problem could
OL,20,Fhave a big impact on poorer claimants. 
